Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:19.57,EDJP 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\fs-2}darkness, take me in soundlessly holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:27.37,EDJP 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\fs-2}In the depths silent world, long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:38.47,EDJP 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\fs-2}all that will remain broken heart, farewell
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:44.56,EDJP 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\fs-2}Memories of better days
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:53.82,EDJP 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\fs-2}locked within in hopes that we will remember
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:19:08.46,EDJP 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\fs-2}someday we may wake to find sunrise
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:16.25,EDJP 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\fs-2}Sliver sky, falls upon you and I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:23.64,EDJP 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\fs-2}another hope fades away into night
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:31.35,EDJP 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\fs-2}distant melodies, a sweet lullaby
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:40.57,EDJP 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\fs-2}will lead me to you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:48.04,EDJP 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\fs-2}Firefly, glows upon you and I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:57.09,EDJP 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\fs-2}another hope fades away into the lonely night
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:20:05.80,EDJP 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\fs-2}when morning comes, the gentle voice will lead you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:13.52,EDJP 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\fs-2}to the light
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:11.36,EDCN 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2}漫漫長夜 黎明之光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:19.57,EDCN 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2}無聲黑暗 靜靜永駐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:27.37,EDCN 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2}寂靜深淵 時光消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:38.47,EDCN 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2}心若刀絞 輕訴永別
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:44.56,EDCN 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2}往昔回憶 歷歷在目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:53.82,EDCN 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2}緊鎖希望 永記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:19:08.46,EDCN 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2}終有一日 夜醒日出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:16.25,EDCN 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2}銀墜天穹 落於你我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:23.64,EDCN 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2}淒淒期盼 黯淡入夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:31.35,EDCN 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2}遙遙音律 甜美夜曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:40.57,EDCN 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2}指引你我 相見幾何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:48.04,EDCN 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2}螢火之光 點亮前路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:57.09,EDCN 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2}淒淒期盼 黯淡孤夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:20:05.80,EDCN 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2}清晨已至 耳畔柔聲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:13.52,EDCN 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be2}引導其路 燦爛光明
